5. Lab 3: Linux Hardening
Step 1. Update packages
sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade -y
Step 2. Check sudo users
getent group sudo
Step 3. Check SSH configuration
sudo grep -E 'PermitRootLogin|PasswordAuthentication' /etc/ssh/sshd_config
Step 4. Disable root SSH login
sudo nano /etc/ssh/sshd_config
Step 5. Apply SSH change
PermitRootLogin no
Step 6. Restart SSH service
sudo systemctl restart ssh
Step 7. Check password policy
sudo cat /etc/login.defs
Step 8. Check important permissions
ls -l /etc/shadow
Step 9. Enable UFW firewall
sudo ufw enable
Step 10. Allow SSH
sudo ufw allow ssh
Step 11. Verify firewall
sudo ufw status verbose
All changes must be reversible. Students must document each modification.
